This repository is supplementary code for the paper "Variational Bayesian Methods for Cognitive Science" (2019).
There's code here for estimating mean-field posteriors of a bivariate normal's mean and Brown and Heatchote's Linear Ballistic Accumulator.

If you find this code useful, please cite our paper: Galdo, M., Bahg, G., & Turner, B. M. (2019). Variational Bayesian methods for cognitive science. Psychological methods.
